OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fmostly cloudy this evening and tonight
OL,7,Fwith frequent showers, some heavy, and
OL,8,Fa few drier clearer intervals. Mainly
OL,9,Flight winds, but quite breezy along
OL,10,Fthe Solway Coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,13,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,14,FWinds will be mainly light in the
OL,15,Fmorning, freshening in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
