OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBrighter
OL,6,FFriday with sunny intervals and some
OL,7,Fshowers Friday. Rain spreading from
OL,8,Fwest on Saturday, turning heavy later,
OL,9,Fclearing in evening. Occasional rain
OL,10,Fand bright intervals on Sunday.
OL,11,FOccasionally windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
